<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" contentStyleType="text/css" data-diagram-type="CLASS" height="328px" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="width:790px;height:328px;background:#FFFFFF;" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 790 328" width="790px" zoomAndPan="magnify"><?plantuml 1.2026.3beta6?><defs/><g><g class="legend" data-source-line="1"><rect fill="#DDDDDD" height="287.0469" rx="7.5" ry="7.5" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1;" width="759.376" x="12" y="22"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="399.3008" x="17" y="39.9951">The plugin you are using seems to generated a bad URL.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="295.8867" x="17" y="56.292">This URL does not look like DEFLATE data.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="367.6641" x="17" y="72.5889">It looks like your plugin is using HUFFMAN encoding.</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="88.8857">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="671.7061" x="17" y="105.1826">This means you have now to add an header ~1 to your data. For example, you have to change:</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="557.3408" x="17" y="121.4795">http://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/png/png/JSmz2W9138RXFgVuc7uhUrcmjd...</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="14.0547" x="17" y="137.7764">to</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="577.9785" x="17" y="154.0732">http://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/png/~1png/JSmz2W9138RXFgVuc7uhUrcmjd...</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="170.3701">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="138.2773" x="17" y="186.667">It will work this way</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="428.1484" x="17" y="202.9639">You may contact the PlantUML team at plantuml@gmail.com</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="749.376" x="17" y="219.2607">But you should also probably contact the plugin authors you are currently using and send them this image</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="235.5576">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="232.5449" x="17" y="251.8545">For the record, here is your data:</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="4.4502" x="17" y="268.1514">&#160;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="691.291" x="17" y="284.4482">png/JSmz2W9138RXFgVuc7uhUrcmjd7r024Jbe7vaIHJYGVo75vCjB9zUNXN3xQOhHAnn31iAgR1LfXC</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="669.6348" x="17" y="300.7451">9RZlLP6sug6DaHNNQNqupkzNBZ8yuK70T1LsHRhetSPktDWGNvd0ZjlfGFXROrcEl_WaMhNdsUe7</text></g><?plantuml-src ZLFBLjim4DthA-O3E4u2BOQiI0WXf8u9Xf30fcTY3RQ9BBbwn2GBlhsoKyhffkr2Ej8yxhqp8mdAI7Bsa1DKmcM5X9roW9h0cK9cO8XA0rQ13oEDbZWWh9738ea2drQOvWHSaG6fB0YbDY2A3S7eQXmD7gw0eyM0tHnSvk3p7Fg3poCSg2QByNWsY85aghWt1Eo0Nn9AqyhASKkUfMxq8FTA9EI4d3IyznfR2zlomLXfe3SiAq57dxa-9irHPjHdkRLLlzEfwpge14hhIX6agknyN3gLpDerlI_tnylptibPiXfdZouDNRxGQVdAWo1WLlqVqdlltrXDa-f22AYLte1jQgznnvwy-X9ta2ffCRNUGJ1li1Up22nX2MZXW-mYAx5e-TdGsRPoaoidVBE4KL1fjSQr-1Firo3GsLnfy_i1f4vhajO77-Q3alldu3UVKnxa5ILcn5ZJx0P8KweqF_93yUc5-Pn7dx6_bn_gxl6NwPh2BTvCfa_NZohykhry7Pxl5_4gFdcxkyqd0obFUiKWIthHo-gIdIVF8fgV6fUTZd0IntVn3rTjzl7m-MpdleNTXrva9abEzdw-iQFbTRpbtUTNyN8zNYMtEhqItvSuosDk5XGoNvPeVy9F?></g></svg>